<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Disgorge" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Disgorge,</orth> to vomit: <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.7.69" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 7, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.7.69" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 7, 69</bibl>. Per. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.0." default="NO" valid="yes">III Prol. 48</bibl>. Followed by <emph>of,</emph> == to empty by vomiting: <cit><quote>so didst thou d. thy glutton bosom of the royal Richard,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.3.97" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 3, 97</bibl></cit>.
